snippet.title: Pinball Soccer '98 - Pin-Ball Games - Intro
snippet.description: The introductory sequence from the pinball simulation Pinball Soccer '98 for MS Windows.  Originally by Pin-Ball Games but more commonly seen on compilations by Rebellion/GT Select/GT Interactive Europe.
